snippet.title: [Bless Online] Assassin Trailer - Become the Shadows
snippet.description:
The highly anticipated Assassin class is here with the August 8 update! 

Watch out for daggers and sneak attacks while you check out the stealthy new class in action in our Assassin trailer!
